与 EDP 屏不同，LVDS 屏的 Timing 写在 DTS 文件中，在 `kernel/arch/arm64/boot/dts/rockchip/{{lvds_dts}}` 中可以看到以下语句：

```
disp_timings: display-timings {
    native-mode = <&timing0>;
    timing0: timing0 {
        clock-frequency = <166000000>; //166000000 @50
        hactive = <800>;
        vactive = <1280>;
        hsync-len = <10>;              //20, 50
        hback-porch = <100>;           //50, 56
        hfront-porch = <1580>;         //50, 30 //1580
        vsync-len = <10>;
        vback-porch = <25>;
        vfront-porch = <10>;
        hsync-active = <0>;
        vsync-active = <0>;
        de-active = <0>;
        pixelclk-active = <0>;
    };
};

```

